            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My Son & Daughter Shivansh & Ovee Bharti are very energetic and enthusiastic after the admission in Walnut school. Every activity is booster for my children. The result has came, just a few days before my daughter got a Gold and my Son got a Silver at district level karate championship. My daughter got selected for next level that is state level under 6 year age.\n\nThe sports activities are very helpful to child for health building and Mr.Tushar Pawar sports teacher of Fursungi branch make everything to involve the students in sports activities.\nThans to all Walnut teacher and the management for making positive changes in my children.\n\nAll the best!!!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
