          },
          "datePublished": "2023-07-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Walnut school one of the best school i have ever came across with its unique features , which gives equal importance to studies as well as other extra and co curricular activities which ensures the overall development of children's. As a teacher it an great experience to work with walnut school as it teaches us to work in team and co-operate among each other. Both teaching and non teaching staff is equally supportive.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Walnut School - Shivane"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Anita Kudale"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-17",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Walnut school has a positive environment and very welcoming atmosphere. The school has well-structured premises, the infrastructure is spacious and has a lot of open space for multiple activities. Walnut school has unique features such as subject wise classrooms, no bag concept; everyday sports, computational thinking which makes schooling a very placid experience. The bag-less feature makes every child enter school burden free with all the enthusiasm and curiosity to learn something new each day. They have a planned curricular and co-curricular program that focuses on overall development of every child. The differential learning approach helps every child understand and inculcate all concepts with ease. Will strongly recommend Walnut School to every parent who want, their child to have a stress free and fun filled learning experience.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Walnut School - Shivane"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Hemant Kamalakar"
          },
          "datePublished": "2023-06-03",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As an outgoing parent, I cannot praise Walnut School enough for their exceptional focus on discipline and conduct. From day one, my child was immersed in an environment that fostered respect and responsibility. The school's strong disciplinary policies and consistent enforcement created a safe and orderly atmosphere. The teachers' dedication to instilling good values and manners in the students is truly remarkable. I am confident that Walnut School has prepared my child not just academically, but also for a bright future as a respectful and well-behaved individual.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
